{"tid":1016654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗俄野心 波蘭斥資$32.5億購美製火箭系統","createTime":"2019-02-11T01:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T10:29:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c02e79f3e2b5dd7a10ed1f94db717f54118d18","tid":1016654,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190211/large/1549834982_e02f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190211%2Flarge%2F1549834982_e02f.jpg&h=db874267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波蘭和俄羅斯近年關係緊張，波蘭尋求華府支持華沙抗衡俄羅斯對東歐的軍事威脅。波蘭防長布拉斯札克（Mariusz Blaszczak）表示，波蘭將斥資4.14億美元（32.5億港元）從美國購入HIMARS火箭系統，<br />\n布拉斯札克稱，雙方將會在本周三簽約，預料系統將在2023年付運，稱系統將可「顯著提升波蘭軍隊的戰力」。去年3月，波蘭已斥資47.5億美元（372億港元）購買美國的愛國者防空導彈，又提議美軍在境內興建永久基地。<br />\n「高機動性多管火箭系統」（HIMARS）是由軍火商洛歇馬丁製造，它是一個裝在戰術軍車骨架的火箭炮發射系統，其發射角度較高，可令爆炸範圍較小但命中率高，避免誤炸，效果據稱與精準空襲相若。系統可發射6枚射程70公里的導引火箭，或1枚射程300公里的導彈。<br />\n法新社／中央社／《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190211/59245313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59245313&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo5y%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=50eaa6fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59245313&h=d504bf23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190211/59245313</a>"},{"pid":"f3be475b58063a8410d40e4abbdf51cf8562f5e9","tid":1016654,"uid":224952,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"野咩心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d47960b419fefefeb48e9a50166e694d39761f7","tid":1016654,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"呢枝野好勁, RANGE 打到 300KM<br />\n<br />\n彈導導彈以外, 就係呢枝野打到最遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.armyrecognition.com/images/stories/news/2018/february/Romania_approves_purchase_of_US_M142_HIMARS_missile_rocket_launchers_925_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armyrecognition.com%2Fimages%2Fstories%2Fnews%2F2018%2Ffebruary%2FRomania_approves_purchase_of_US_M142_HIMARS_missile_rocket_launchers_925_001.jpg&h=d3073cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.armyrecognition.com/images/stories/news/2018/february/Romania_approves_purchase_of_US_M142_HIMARS_missile_rocket_launchers_925_002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armyrecognition.com%2Fimages%2Fstories%2Fnews%2F2018%2Ffebruary%2FRomania_approves_purchase_of_US_M142_HIMARS_missile_rocket_launchers_925_002.jpg&h=5d883b54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f87960c2bd25aa7da4fdde0946233fe3ec1713c","tid":1016654,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:18:23.000Z","msg":"啱啦 賤俄遲早俾人圍摳 深仇血債一定要報"},{"pid":"5bf75173760d185ea3f68d14f6b70cb25df76d1e","tid":1016654,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"波蘭靠哂侵侵e八年穩定國防<br />\n奧狗馬班民主狗賣左佢地好多年"},{"pid":"2a74551ec70a9acefb01213b935ef00a85b8bcfd","tid":1016654,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bf75173760d185ea3f68d14f6b70cb25df76d1e","tid":1016654,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"波蘭靠哂侵侵e八年穩定國防<br />\n奧狗馬班民主狗賣左佢地好多年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"靠近俄羅斯既國家都好親美親北約<br />\n個個驚被打亡國<br />\n馬其頓、波蘭、羅馬尼亞、波羅的海三國<br />\n<br />\n係德國死肥婆及其ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 國民先唔識死, 話要親支拒美"}]}